name: search_capability_skill
description: Comprehensive multi-source search and information retrieval capability for analyzing technical questions, diagnosing faults, and gathering specifications across multiple domains

triggers:
  - User asks about equipment parameters, fault codes, or technical specifications
  - Need to retrieve historical cases, maintenance records, or troubleshooting procedures
